text: James Murray Vickerman (May 1, 1931 â€“ January 19, 2021) was an American politician. He was a member of the Minnesota Senate from 1987 to 2011. He was a member of the Minnesota Democratic-Farmer-Labor Party. He was born in Tracy, Minnesota. Vickerman died on January 19, 2021 in Marshall, Minnesota at the age of 89. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2021 deaths Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Politicians from Minnesota Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians
